## DBsubject(Algebra)
## DBchapter(Rational equations and functions)
## DBsection(Graphs of rational functions)
## Institution(Loyola University Chicago and Fort Lewis College)
## Author(Adam Spiegler and Paul Pearson)
## Level(3)
